{"id":38,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":38,"title":"2 Nephi 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Jacob continues reading from Isaiah: In the last days, the Lord will comfort Zion and gather Israel—The redeemed will come to Zion amid great joy—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.1?span=51.1-52.2"},"Isaiah 51 and 52:1–2"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.1","order":"05.13.008.3910"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Hearken"],"unto me, ye that follow after righteousness. Look unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"rock"],"from whence ye are hewn, and to the hole of the pit from whence ye are digged."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.2","order":"05.13.008.3911"},["b","2"],"Look unto Abraham, your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"father"],", and unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Sarah"],", she that bare you; for I called him alone, and blessed him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.3","order":"05.13.008.3912"},["b","3"],"For the Lord shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"comfort"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Zion"],", he will comfort all her waste places; and he will make her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"wilderness"],"like",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"Eden"],", and her desert like the garden of the Lord. Joy and gladness shall be found therein, thanksgiving and the voice of melody."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.4","order":"05.13.008.3913"},["b","4"],"Hearken unto me, my people; and give ear unto me, O my nation; for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"law"],"shall proceed from me, and I will make my judgment to rest for a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"light"],"for the people."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.5","order":"05.13.008.3914"},["b","5"],"My righteousness is near; my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"salvation"],"is gone forth, and mine arm shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"judge"],"the people. The",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"isles"],"shall wait upon me, and on mine arm shall they trust."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.6","order":"05.13.008.3915"},["b","6"],"Lift up your eyes to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"heavens"],", and look upon the earth beneath; for the heavens shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"vanish"],"away like smoke, and the earth shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"wax old"],"like a garment; and they that dwell therein shall die in like manner. But my salvation shall be forever, and my righteousness shall not be abolished."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.7","order":"05.13.008.3916"},["b","7"],"Hearken unto me, ye that know righteousness, the people in whose heart I have written my law,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"fear"],"ye not the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"reproach"],"of men, neither be ye afraid of their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"revilings"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.8","order":"05.13.008.3917"},["b","8"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"moth"],"shall eat them up like a garment, and the worm shall eat them like wool. But my righteousness shall be forever, and my salvation from generation to generation."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.9","order":"05.13.008.3918"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Awake"],", awake! Put on",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"strength"],", O arm of the Lord; awake as in the ancient days. Art thou not he that hath cut",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"Rahab"],", and wounded the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"dragon"],"?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.10","order":"05.13.008.3919"},["b","10"],"Art thou not he who hath dried the sea, the waters of the great deep; that hath made the depths of the sea a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"way"],"for the ransomed to pass over?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.11","order":"05.13.008.3920"},["b","11"],"Therefore, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"redeemed"],"of the Lord shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"return"],", and come with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"singing"],"unto Zion; and everlasting joy and holiness shall be upon their heads; and they shall obtain gladness and joy; sorrow and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"mourning"],"shall flee away."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.12","order":"05.13.008.3921"},["b","12"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"I"],"am he; yea, I am he that comforteth you. Behold, who art thou, that thou shouldst be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"afraid"],"of man, who shall die, and of the son of man, who shall be made like unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"grass"],"?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.13","order":"05.13.008.3922"},["b","13"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"forgettest"],"the Lord thy maker, that hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"stretched"],"forth the heavens, and laid the foundations of the earth, and hast feared continually every day, because of the fury of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"oppressor"],", as if he were ready to destroy? And where is the fury of the oppressor?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.14","order":"05.13.008.3923"},["b","14"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"captive"],"exile hasteneth, that he may be loosed, and that he should not die in the pit, nor that his bread should fail."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.15","order":"05.13.008.3924"},["b","15"],"But I am the Lord thy God, whose",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"waves"],"roared; the Lord of Hosts is my name."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.16","order":"05.13.008.3925"},["b","16"],"And I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"put"],"my words in thy mouth, and have covered thee in the shadow of mine hand, that I may plant the heavens and lay the foundations of the earth, and say unto Zion: Behold, thou art my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"people"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.17","order":"05.13.008.3926"},["b","17"],"Awake, awake, stand up, O Jerusalem, which hast drunk at the hand of the Lord the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"cup"],"of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"fury"],"—thou hast drunken the dregs of the cup of trembling wrung out—"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.18","order":"05.13.008.3927"},["b","18"],"And none to guide her among all the sons she hath brought forth; neither that taketh her by the hand, of all the sons she hath brought up."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.19","order":"05.13.008.3928"},["b","19"],"These two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"sons"],"are come unto thee, who shall be sorry for thee—thy desolation and destruction, and the famine and the sword—and by whom shall I comfort thee?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.20","order":"05.13.008.3929"},["b","20"],"Thy sons have fainted, save these two; they lie at the head of all the streets; as a wild bull in a net, they are full of the fury of the Lord, the rebuke of thy God."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.21","order":"05.13.008.3930"},["b","21"],"Therefore hear now this, thou afflicted, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"drunken"],", and not with wine:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.22","order":"05.13.008.3931"},["b","22"],"Thus saith thy Lord, the Lord and thy God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"pleadeth"],"the cause of his people; behold, I have taken out of thine hand the cup of trembling, the dregs of the cup of my fury; thou shalt no more drink it again."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.23","order":"05.13.008.3932"},["b","23"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"I"],"will put it into the hand of them that afflict thee; who have said to thy soul: Bow down, that we may go over—and thou hast laid thy body as the ground and as the street to them that went over."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.24","order":"05.13.008.3933"},["b","24"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Awake"],", awake, put on thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"strength"],", O",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"Zion"],"; put on thy beautiful garments, O Jerusalem, the holy city; for henceforth there shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_24d"},"no more"],"come into thee the uncircumcised and the unclean."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.25","order":"05.13.008.3934"},["b","25"],"Shake thyself from the dust; arise, sit down, O Jerusalem; loose thyself from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"bands"],"of thy neck, O captive daughter of Zion."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.1a","order":"05.13.008.3935"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.1.1-23"},"Isa. 51:1 (1–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1"},"2 Ne. 7:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.1b","order":"05.13.008.3937"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"Abraham and Sarah; see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.2"},"v. 2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"TG Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.2a","order":"05.13.008.3939"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/17.4.1-8"},"Gen. 17:4 (1–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.64"},"D&C 109:64"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.49"},"132:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.2b","order":"05.13.008.3941"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/24.36"},"Gen. 24:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.3a","order":"05.13.008.3943"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"TG Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.3b","order":"05.13.008.3945"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.3c","order":"05.13.008.3947"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/35.2.1-2,6-7"},"Isa. 35:2 (1–2, 6–7)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.3d","order":"05.13.008.3949"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eden"},"Eden"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.4a","order":"05.13.008.3951"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/2.3"},"Isa. 2:3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-law-of"},"TG God, Law of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.4b","order":"05.13.008.3953"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.5a","order":"05.13.008.3955"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-savior"},"TG Jesus Christ, Savior"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.5b","order":"05.13.008.3957"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.5c","order":"05.13.008.3959"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.20"},"2 Ne. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.6a","order":"05.13.008.3961"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.10"},"2 Pet. 3:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.6b","order":"05.13.008.3963"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.13"},"Isa. 13:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.6c","order":"05.13.008.3965"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.26.25-28"},"Ps. 102:26 (25–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.7a","order":"05.13.008.3967"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/1.17"},"Deut. 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/56.4.4,11"},"Ps. 56:4 (4, 11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/118.6"},"118:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.9"},"D&C 122:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peer-influence"},"TG Peer Influence"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.7b","order":"05.13.008.3969"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.7c","order":"05.13.008.3971"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hate"},"TG Hate"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.8a","order":"05.13.008.3973"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.9"},"Isa. 50:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.9a","order":"05.13.008.3975"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.1"},"Isa. 52:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.9b","order":"05.13.008.3977"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/113.8.7-8"},"D&C 113:8 (7–8)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"TG Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/8.9c","order":"05.13.008.3979"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.10"},"Ps. 89:10"],";",["a.scripture